---
import T7Layout from '../layouts/T7Layout.astro';
import MidPageCta from '../components/MidPageCta.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
import { breadcrumbSchema } from '../lib/schema';

const title = 'About';
const description =
  'UK Mortgages Worldwide is a UK mortgage broker specialising in expats, non-UK residents, and people with foreign income.';

const schemas = [
  breadcrumbSchema([
    { name: 'Home', path: '/' },
    { name: 'About' },
  ]),
];
---

<T7Layout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="About UK Mortgages Worldwide"
  eyebrow="ABOUT"
  schemas={schemas}
>
  <p>
    UK Mortgages Worldwide is a UK mortgage broker specialising in expats,
    non-UK residents, and people with foreign income.
  </p>

  <h2>Why this site exists</h2>
  <p>
    Most UK mortgage advice is built for UK residents on PAYE income. The
    moment a client lives abroad, earns in a foreign currency, or holds a
    non-UK passport, the high-street lender list collapses. Standard
    practice across the industry is to apply a 20% haircut to non-GBP
    income, then turn the case down because the affordability no longer
    works.
  </p>
  <p>
    There is a better way. A small group of specialist lenders take foreign
    income at face value, lend to non-UK residents on standard rates, and
    treat expat applicants as a category they actually want to serve.
    Knowing which lender to approach for which situation is the entire job.
  </p>
  <p>
    This site exists to put that knowledge in front of the people searching
    for it, in plain language, without lender lists or generic advice that
    does not survive contact with a real case.
  </p>

  <h2>How enquiries work</h2>
  <p>
    When you send an enquiry, it lands with our team at Mortgage One. A
    broker reviews the case, picks up the phone or replies on WhatsApp,
    and walks you through what is achievable. There is no panel and no
    third-party handover. The person reading your enquiry is the person
    who will arrange your mortgage.
  </p>

  <h2>Firm details</h2>
  <p>
    UK Mortgages Worldwide is a website operated by Mortgage One, a trading
    style of Sandsea Capital Ltd, an appointed representative of Quilter
    Financial Services Limited, which is authorised and regulated by the
    Financial Conduct Authority. Financial Conduct Authority Register No.
    440703.
  </p>
  <p>
    Sandsea Capital Ltd is registered in England and Wales, Company No.
    11374947. Registered office: 555-557 Cranbrook Road, Gants Hill,
    Ilford, Essex, England IG2 6HE.
  </p>

  <MidPageCta variant="hero" />

  <ContactForm />
</T7Layout>
